John A. Power is a former English professional &lt;a href="rugby%20league"&gt;rugby league&lt;/a&gt; footballer (born in &lt;a href="Rochdale"&gt;Rochdale&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="Greater%20Manchester"&gt;Greater Manchester&lt;/a&gt;, England).
Career ending injury.
John was just 18 when he suffered a devastating spinal cord injury, while playing for Oldham RLFC 'A' team. It ended his promising career as a professional rugby player.
